snippet.title: Dream Walker
snippet.description: Enter a surreal dream world as Carrol, a dream walker on a quest to save her husband from the evil spirit named Sandman. As the Sandman strives to take over one’s mind he can use it to break into the real world and cause incomprehensible havoc! Walk through nightmares and help your husband defeat his fears in this captivating hidden object adventure!
